    <item>
      <title>新加坡核心通胀率自 2022 年以来首次放缓至 2.9%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/singapore-core-inflation-slows-below-3-first-time-since-2022</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡六月份核心通胀率的降幅超过预期，使得央行有空间集中精力保护这个贸易依赖型经济免受全球冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-23/singapore-core-inflation-slows-below-3-first-time-since-2022</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 23 Jul 2024 05:00:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>供应链受创导致生产放缓，保时捷利润出现警告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/porsche-cuts-full-year-revenue-forecast-on-parts-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保时捷股份公司 (Porsche AG) 股价出现有史以来最大跌幅，此前这家豪华汽车制造商下调了今年的业绩预期，并表示铝制零部件短缺可能导致其停止生产部分车型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-22/porsche-cuts-full-year-revenue-forecast-on-parts-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 22:53:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
